# The New Founding Family

What would the Founding Fathers do in our situation? This question is as relevant as ever, as we are in a major turning point in human history.

Never before has there been such a juxtiposition between what is and what could be. We have been living in an age a static processes and procedures. While we increase automation, we become ensnared by others using these tools, with the lure of decadence. Our oppressors, ultimately, are the ones that have been providing these advances.
